<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="T" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Timorous" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Timorous,</orth> full of fear, timid: <cit><quote>the t. flying hare,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ven 674" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 674</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the t. yelping of the hounds,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ven 674" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 674</bibl></cit> <cit><quote>like a t. thief,</quote> <bibl n="shak. aww 2.5.86" default="NO" valid="yes">All's II, 5, 86</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>sings heavy music to my t. soul,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 4.2.40" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A IV, 2, 40</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>t. deer,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 4.2.40" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A IV, 2, 40</bibl></cit> <cit><quote>t. wretch,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 1.1.231" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C I, 1, 231</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>his t. dreams,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 4.1.85" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 1, 85</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>with like t. accent and dire yell,</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 1.1.75" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. I, 1, 75</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>